{"tid":1030373,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[海賊王] 劇場版STAMPEDE第二彈預告片 以及 第934話情報 公佈！","createTime":"2019-02-21T01:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T00:46:50.000Z","uid":130563,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd90c13aa45470fabbd801aebc35fcbaa771e71","tid":1030373,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T01:48:17.000Z","msg":"劇場版STAMPEDE第二彈預告片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-f3_oA0uwY0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-f3_oA0uwY0&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=841f3320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-f3_oA0uwY0</a><br />\n<br />\n尾田身份為【原作+監修】<br />\n新角色巴雷特（前羅傑海賊團成員，魔鬼後嗣）、費斯塔（戰爭發動者，慶典大師）<br />\n羅、 斯莫克、達斯琪、巴基﹑亞爾麗塔等人登場！！<br />\n<br />\n宣傳語還提到【尋找羅傑留下的寶藏】的關鍵詞。<br />\n路飛最後喊的是巴雷特的名字。<br />\n尾田：【要是沒有20週年這個名義我是不會讓做這樣的電影的。因為肯定超級有趣啊】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cett1Yw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcett1Yw.jpg&h=203c6a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H0Vwfix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH0Vwfix.jpg&h=77f4c141&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nfrom: TALKOP"},{"pid":"26735c287269a2f4229d09d9a28cba8aaab0b5f2","tid":1030373,"uid":130563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T01:50:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>海賊王934話情報：</strong><br />\n標題： 花之豹五郎<br />\n扉頁是烏索普躺在野餐布上，周圍都是鸚鵡。<br />\n<br />\n和之國地圖：<br />\n以花之都地區為中心，左上方是希美地區，左下方是兔丼地區，勞改採礦場在這裡，<br />\n再西邊是九里地區，從上到下是頭山，博羅町，編笠村，<br />\n花之都右邊兩個地區分別坐落著北之墓場和刃武港，<br />\n地圖最下方是鬼之島。<br />\n<br />\n路飛被吃了羊駝Smile果實的看守威脅，表示路飛戴著海樓石的手銬是不可能逃獄的，敢反抗就砍手。<br />\n礦裡的老爺子被一個六條腿的看守毆打，慌亂中似乎吞下了什麼，被守衛注意到 還是路飛戴著手銬去救人，<br />\n結果未知，結尾是三災裡的Queen來到了礦坑監獄。<br />\n<br />\n下週休刊，這周海賊一共15頁，去掉扉頁14，無跨頁。"},{"pid":"ff2195d5d6507b35ce90a5a306190d54ee24b6bb","tid":1030373,"uid":130563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T01:56:29.000Z","msg":"這是羅等角色首次在劇場版中登場！！<br />\n目前公佈的大Boss--道格拉斯‧巴雷特<br />\n身份是前羅傑海賊團成員、『魔鬼後嗣』！！<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇Boss個樣好似D幹部級嘅樣咁...<br />\n但係個頭銜令我有D興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8121e7390a2d9b35fd5b110be0f6bdc8c67873cb","tid":1030373,"uid":130563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T02:43:15.000Z","msg":"大圖：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd2f3c6e6793716512e73b7aa30f555c0dd5abc","tid":1030373,"uid":94819,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:02:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fedaba05560cbe9552135bac255ca9d51ef32b87","tid":1030373,"uid":74228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"有羅份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8a57e2ff3d57cc654c6ae9a3ab6c280cf70a1b","tid":1030373,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fedaba05560cbe9552135bac255ca9d51ef32b87","tid":1030373,"uid":74228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"有羅份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"個設計睇落唔似會多戲份，分分鐘好似上一套薩波咁，純出下場。"},{"pid":"d3d4d667eb650bfb62068ae2e065f3e572439799","tid":1030373,"uid":81919,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:23:41.000Z","msg":"完全封鎖"},{"pid":"464ab91c64f254128318af19caef36bd01e566b0","tid":1030373,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fbd2f3c6e6793716512e73b7aa30f555c0dd5abc","tid":1030373,"uid":94819,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:02:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:31:17.000Z","msg":"作為羅傑成員個樣太後生"},{"pid":"58eb9221179e3c175d6b3c98f595c2995ce9de99","tid":1030373,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:38:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90e6c0ab82c21d07dbca4c13927095bfa980d890","tid":1030373,"uid":130563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:55:19.000Z","msg":"劇場版嘅簡介：<br />\n由海賊舉舉辦的，為海賊而辦的世界頂尖的慶典 海賊萬博會。<br />\n路飛等草帽一夥收到了被稱作「慶典大師」的萬博會主辦人布埃納‧費斯塔寄來的請柬。<br />\n<br />\n被一路引導到會場後，看到富麗堂皇的亭子星羅密佈，<br />\n以最惡世代為首的眾多海賊匯聚一堂，氣氛空前熱烈。<br />\n萬博會的重頭戲是「尋找海賊王（羅傑）遺留的寶藏」。<br />\n由渴望獲得寶藏名揚四海的海賊們引發的財寶爭奪戰拉開序幕！<br />\n<br />\n然而，在讓海賊們熱血沸騰的萬博會背後，<br />\n佈滿了別名「最邪惡的戰爭發動者」費斯塔的凶行，連想把海賊們一網打盡的海軍也展開了行動&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n左右時代霸權的財寶爭奪戰持續白熱化，<br />\n突然，原羅傑海賊團被稱作「「魔鬼」後嗣」的男人道格拉斯‧巴雷特闖入。<br />\n化為威脅路飛等人的存在擋在他們面前！<br />\n<br />\n瘋狂的海賊、打算終結此事的海軍，<br />\n另外連王下七武海、革命軍也來參戰。不分敵我的大亂鬥開幕。<br />\n財寶爭奪戰和海賊萬博會一味地陷入無法預測的大混亂局面！！"},{"pid":"273280bd41fecb90414133a511f1b0cb8c8bb9be","tid":1030373,"uid":130563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T03:56:49.000Z","msg":"睇嚟羅會有一定戲份，分分鐘仲會有基德。"},{"pid":"71c6f67c8586b2c5442fa185ec3238305a12a6b3","tid":1030373,"uid":61372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:00:53.000Z","msg":"上次果套黃金垃圾到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c98a1412193161109a29ca892eeb023ff021377","tid":1030373,"uid":174654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T04:05:15.000Z","msg":"條預告睇咗等於冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估唔到會用前羅傑嘅成員做boss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n羅 巴基 斯摩格同達絲琪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7740091544f039ce2687db