"巴基船長都係羅傑海賊團前成員"},{"pid":"719191dfa5f0e91397fb71af928d188a06222ee4","tid":1030373,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:25:19.000Z","msg":"原來1月已經有劇場版STAMPEDE嘅彩蛋。<br />\n海賊萬博會--今次劇場版的背景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGOhWRn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGOhWRn.jpg&h=94e15c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iquhcpJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiquhcpJ.jpg&h=348742aa&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}